		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi, i have a question, but i am not completely sure if i am posting this in the right place.<br /><br />I found out that Akumajō Special: Boku Dracula-kun is using the Ines mapper 23, this is a mapper that is almost not supported, is there any &quot;easy&quot; way to change the mapper.<br />I am asking this because i want to play it on the NES mini and it is not supporting mapper 23.

		

		</td>
