		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Oh these Konami mappers...<br />They seem pretty difficult to hack.<br />AFAIK, Begalad did a Japanese Contra hack but give up on Gradius 2.<br />And he's a pretty experienced hacker!<br />When someone with his knowledge gives up this kind of project, I think the possibilities of a hack like this to suffice are very thin.<br />Does Nes mini supports MMC 5?<br />This could be a little easier to hack. <br />But I think the best option is the Rainwarrior's option 2, since this would open the path for many more games and many more mappers.

		

		</td>
